{"tid":2105902,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[接受度測試] 澳門明天用健康碼限制離境, 如果香港都跟隨,接唔接受到?","createTime":"2020-07-13T03:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T11:35:51.000Z","uid":14918,"like":8,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7d46396d10d00edf331dbced478bfccfef6efa09","tid":2105902,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:13:37.000Z","msg":"澳門明天用健康碼限制離境, <br />\n如果香港都跟隨,接唔接受到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳門新冠病毒應變協調中心今日(12日)宣布，後日(14日)上午6時起，所有乘坐由澳門出發客船和飛機的乘客，必須出示7天內新冠病毒核酸檢測陰性證明，即無確診感染，有關證明可透過澳門健康碼取得，當局指措施是為了保障客船和飛機工作人員及乘客安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E6%B5%B7%E7%A9%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%A2%83-%E9%A0%88%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E-214500821.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25A2%2583-%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2598%258E-214500821.html&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZosx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=af91e023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E6%B5%B7%E7%A9%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%A2%83-%E9%A0%88%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E-214500821.html</a>"},{"pid":"3811a6d1f4e4f041c32d1eeba8649a0f6e231caf","tid":2105902,"uid":37487,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"777:健康碼是圈套"},{"pid":"7d541d2accec32c2be3089410c262dafe0c23b7f","tid":2105902,"uid":168522,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"政府唔比code = 無得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b1c685309827a75146b1e0eb3a930880fce7da","tid":2105902,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:17:47.000Z","msg":"成班豬叫港共加強防疫, 算唔算比劇本港共鎖港限制自由?"},{"pid":"047a6ed06ecb2b5d20df48c9a7fb6a319342982e","tid":2105902,"uid":118346,"like"