"放心一定會咁做。<br />\n中共有心消滅香港人，唔會有人可以阻止。"},{"pid":"e2135795925d9adf388b9c9cd70cc2ac1313de04","tid":2105902,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"基本法出入境自由？"},{"pid":"ca927babefd6d2d175d4c3e16d92e0df9e62081d","tid":2105902,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"健康碼呢家嘢cup水碼黎"},{"pid":"f306f7bda9dc34cb1ed9fcc0c6fe1426d594011c","tid":2105902,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca927babefd6d2d175d4c3e16d92e0df9e62081d","tid":2105902,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"健康碼呢家嘢cup水碼黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"唔止cap水，最重要係阻止香港人隨時走。<br />\n玩絕啲，驗到冇問題，但去到過關出境，一句：「你個健康碼有問題。」就可以唔畀你走。"},{"pid":"3fe3ffd404524c9253fff3c7516fea7cf4bb9f99","tid":2105902,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16f9160f0ee3ae22d84355bbc5cd8fa746af74b0","tid":2105902,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:36:59.000Z","msg":"[警告] 澳門暫停核酸檢查，市民無法取得健康碼離境批文，同時賣港派正積極支持引入健康碼機制，為新疆化作最後準備<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2108527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2108527</a>"},{"pid":"ad49dc1358306b0b32ba34edbf0b7dfbb1652547","tid":2105902,"uid":115184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"好似澳洲咁，出境要拎批文"},{"pid":"98be956556187c1766445fd0a038ee90e943240f","tid":2105902,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12b1c685309827a75146b1e0eb3a930880fce7da","tid":2105902,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:17:47.000Z","msg":"成班豬叫港共加強防疫, 算唔算比劇本港共鎖港限制自由?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"唔覺，就算佢押後立法會都係用疫情嚴重，選舉會危害公眾利益做理由，唔太關係咪香港人叫政府加強防疫事，成日話人豬豬豬，其實都唔見得諗野有幾獨到"},{"pid":"4aa6bc1e928ef856c833588c2d